trans-unit.source: Specifies implementation requirements for XML MTOM readers that derive from this interface.
trans-unit.target: Anger implementeringskrav för XML MTOM-läsare som härleds från det här gränssnittet.

trans-unit.source: Specifies initialization requirements for XML MTOM readers that read a stream.
trans-unit.target: Anger initieringen krav för XML MTOM-läsare som läser en dataström.

trans-unit.source: The stream from which to read.
The possible character encodings of the stream.
Can be <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if the MIME type is present in the document being read.
trans-unit.target: Kan vara <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> om MIME-typen finns i dokumentet läses.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XmlDictionaryReaderQuotas> to apply to the reader.
The maximum allowed size of the buffer.
The delegate to use when an <xref uid="langword_csharp_onClose" name="onClose" href=""></xref> event happens.
trans-unit.target: Delegaten ska använda en <xref uid="langword_csharp_onClose" name="onClose" href=""> </xref> händelsen inträffar.

trans-unit.source: Specifies initialization requirements for XML MTOM readers that read a buffer.
trans-unit.target: Anger initieringen krav för XML MTOM-läsare som läser en buffert.

trans-unit.source: The buffer from which to read.
trans-unit.target: Den buffert som ska läsas från.

trans-unit.source: The starting position from which to read in `buffer`.
trans-unit.target: Startpositionen som ska läsas i från `buffer`.

trans-unit.source: The number of bytes that can be read from `buffer`.
trans-unit.target: Antal byte som kan läsas från `buffer`.

trans-unit.source: The possible character encodings of the input.
Can be <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if the MIME type is present in the document being read.
trans-unit.target: Kan vara <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> om MIME-typen finns i dokumentet läses.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XmlDictionaryReaderQuotas> to apply to the reader.
The maximum allowed size of the buffer.
The delegate to use when an <xref uid="langword_csharp_onClose" name="onClose" href=""></xref> event happens.
trans-unit.target: Delegaten ska använda en <xref uid="langword_csharp_onClose" name="onClose" href=""> </xref> händelsen inträffar.
